definitions.definition: To use a thesaurus ; to look for synonyms ; to suggest synonyms.
To use or to mention synonyms; ( often ) to replace words in a text with synonyms in order to disguise plagiarism .

main_definition: ( nonstandard ) To use a thesaurus ; to look for synonyms ; to suggest synonyms.
